Introduced on the web in April 2011,  Bitcoin Gamer offers simple games like:

* coin toss (96% payout)
* roulette (94.7% payout)
* DGBells Penny Slot Machine (94.1% payout)
* dart board (91.7% payout)
* JacksUp - "jacks or better" video poker with up to a 1000:1 return (94.3% payout)

Deposits and wagers of Bitcoins can be as low as 0.01 BTC.  To insure prompt and full payout on all games, players will find that some games have a low house maximum wager.

